# Student Management System

## Description
This is a simple Python command line project to manage student records.
User can add, show, search and delete students.

## Features
- Add Student
- Show Students
- Search Student
- Delete Student

## Requirements
Python must be installed.

## How to Run

1. Open terminal
2. Go to project folder
3. Run command:

python main.py

## Files in Project

main.py
students.json
README.md

